title: More debris but no word on fate of U.S. cargo ship lost off Bahamas
text:
Published By: Baltimore Sun News - Yesterday 
The search for a U.S. cargo ship that was lost during Hurricane Joaquin off the southeastern Bahamas turned up more clues Sunday but no word...
